STATE of North Carolina
v.
Charles Edward HUMPHRIES, Jr. No. 256P15. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Aug. 20, 2015. Charles Edward Humphries, Jr., for Humphries, Charles Edward (Jr.). Robert C. Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State of N.C. Jeff Hunt, District Attorney, for State of N.C.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 22nd of July 2015 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Transylvania County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 20th of August 2015."
